Rio Grande Drilling Co saidits subsidiary, Rio Grande Video, entered into a limitedpartnership agreement with a group of private investors todevelop and operate five Blockbuster Video Superstores inFlorida.    Blockbuster Video Superstores are franchises of BlockbusterEntertainment Corp &lt;BBEC>.    Rio Grande Video will act as general partner, owning 50 pctof the partnership, it said. The company must open 10 storeswithin the next two years to maintain exclusive license rightsin the territory, it said. Reuter&#3;